Hi,
It seems to me that the following code is off-by-one bug.
http://lxr.linux.no/source/net/unix/af_unix.c#L191
http://lxr.linux.no/source/net/unix/af_unix.c?v=2.4.28#L182
I think
((char *)sunaddr)[len]=0;
should be
((char *)sunaddr)[len-1]=0;
Thanks.
